title: MVP and Defensive Player of the Year Predictions, Five Unanswered Questions, and Fantasy Swings
itunes:title: MVP and Defensive Player of the Year Predictions, Five Unanswered Questions, and Fantasy Swings
description:
Prediction Week continues on the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast. Hosts Kay Adams, Michael Robinson, Peter Schrager and Kyle Brandt share their MVP and Defensive Player of the Year predictions. They look at the latest move by the Ravens, what kind of season Ben Roethlisberger will have, and will Tua be the man in Miami?

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network
